&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1136&quot;&gt;Use AI coding tools (e.g. Cursor, Claude Code, GitHub Copilot) as a standard part of your workflow, while developing the judgment to review and validate generated code&lt;/li&gt;
